extendedInfo.description: With nearly 500 practice questions, the Examination for Professional Practice in Psychology Exam Prep app is Upward Mobilityâs focused Android exam preparation application for the EPPP Exam. Your satisfaction is important to us and we have a no questions asked refund policy for all our Android apps. We encourage you to try our application out risk free and let us know by e-mailing info@upwardpro.com if there are any issues.OVERVIEW:The EPPP Exam assesses whether a prospective psychologist has the competency and skills to practice successfully and to be credentialed. Additionally, the exam identifies a working knowledge of patient care, ethical and legal issues, assessing and diagnosing patients, research methods, statistics, and general knowledge of psychology and behavior. By assessing learned knowledge in practical questions, Upward Mobilityâs EPPP Exam Prep will help to successfully bridge the gap between your education and practical patient application.FEATURES:*  Nearly 500 targeted questions.*  Detailed, explanatory answers.*  Exclusive, intuitive interface.*  Study Mode -- Each question is paired with a clear and useful explanation. reviews.title: Good but too easy
reviews.comment: This is a nice app for keeping basic concepts fresh in mind, but the questions are way easier and with obvious wrong answer choices than what would be encountered on the eppp. Also would be nice to have the questions sortable by subject.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Okay but watch for errors
reviews.comment: A found about a half dozen errors and typos. I would only recommend using this to settlement other materials.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Excellent tool to add to your studies
reviews.comment: This is excellent. A great portable study tool that you can use when you find you have a spare moment. I am taking the test soon and what I hear from those that have passed is \"take practice tests! The most the better.\" This can help to do that, inexpensively!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Good collection of 492 items with rationales. Please be careful though as I\'ve found a very few questions are incorrectly scored.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Very handy app, some answers are wrong
reviews.comment: Super handy for studying during brief moments of down time. Super frustrating that some answers are wrong (373, for example - Beth is a high LPC). Far less important, the sliders to select # of items for a test is hard to use.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Excellent quick study tool for minutes of freedom in between. Developer, is there a possibility for also splitting the questions by areas? Thanks!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Worthless
reviews.comment: Has 106 questions, several are wrong. Not really worth it
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Great App for preparing for the EPPP License. A lot of questions (w/ explanations) study phase & exam phase. Well constructed!! Thx.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Helpful but...
reviews.comment: This app is very helpful for exam preparation on the go. However, it would be a much better app if the questions were organized by subject area.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: I took the EPPP last month and passed first try with study materials from 2004 and this app!
reviews.author: A Google User
